		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;504&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1210px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://blog.ddata.fr/p/powerautomate-first-flow/img/004-power-automate-step-2-02.png&#34;
